  <h1>URL Shortener Microservice</h1>

  <p>User stories: </p>

  <ul>
  	<li>I can pass a URL as a parameter after "/new" and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.</li>
  	<li>When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h3>Example creation usage:</h3>
  <code>https://yo-fcc-url-shortener-microservice.glitch.me/new/https://www.google.com</code>
  
  <h3>Example creation output:</h3>
  <code>{ "original_url":"https://www.google.com", "short_url":"https://yo-fcc-url-shortener-microservice.glitch.me/8170" }</code>

  <h3>Usage:</h3>
  <code>https://yo-fcc-url-shortener-microservice.glitch.me/8170</code>

  <h3>Will redirect to:</h3>
  <code>https://www.google.com/</code>
  
